title: Was I supposed to get my ranked rewards or something?
body:
kinda a new player, was just in time to get to silver IV before season 8 ended. I'm honor level 2 and meet the requirements but I have only received the icon border and not the other stuff? 

idk am I stupid or something

replies.body:
There aren't all that many rewards for Silver. If you have received your icons, ranked armour, and previous season border (some of which you may have to activate) then off the top of my head that's about everything.

At any rate, if you submit a ticket to player support they will be able to tell you what rewards you were eligible for, and if you have received all of them: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new
